title: istheelectionover.com
description:
Check here to see if a winner has been projected in the election, with no news or updates to suck you into the chaos.

Some people truly enjoy watching election night coverage. Good for them. This is for everyone else. No news about how it’s going. No analysis. No predictions. No speculation. No conspiracy theories.

 Super silly and simple, but a good nudge for your mental health.
